      "body" : "Before you instantiate XSSFWorkbook, can you paste in this line of code just above:      <code>System.out.println(&quot;Commons IO version: &quot; +          org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils.class.getPackage().getImplemen&zwnj;&#8203;tationVersion());</code>   Also, (depending on whether you&#39;re using maven or gradle), run one of these commands to find out how many versions of commons-io you have: - <code>mvn dependency:tree | grep commons-io</code> - <code>gradle dependencies | grep commons-io</code>"
